# Map & Alert Rules

- Use Google Maps or Mapbox SDK with government-level API key.
- Hotspot aggregation cron job must run nightly.
- Geo-fencing engine must trigger push notifications for civilians inside radius.
- WebSockets must update map sessions in real time.
- Officers can create, edit, and expire hotspot zones.
